name: 21/22 Y1D - Team 11 - Tiki Taradiddles
description:
Become a real cowboy!

Are you ever tired of being the same old you? Go on an adventure with our tiki boy on a quest to become a real cowboy. Jump, dash, and swing through the tiki island. Overcome all the obstacles to obtain your prized possession, something a cowboy can't live without, his hat.
